          <p>
            Bin Collection is a simple iPhone application designed to help users remember bin collection days through:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Local notifications and reminders</li>
            <li>A home screen widget displaying upcoming collection dates</li>
            <li>Management of multiple bin types and collection schedules</li>
            <li>Customizable notification timing</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            The App operates entirely on your device and does not require an internet connection to function.
          </p>
