            <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the App</li>
            <li>Use the App for any commercial purpose</li>
            <li>Distribute, sublicense, or transfer the App to third parties</li>
            <li>Remove or alter any proprietary notices or labels</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p>You are responsible for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Ensuring the accuracy of bin collection schedules you enter</li>
            <li>Verifying collection dates with your local waste management authority</li>
            <li>Keeping your device's date and time settings accurate</li>
            <li>Managing your device's notification settings appropriately</li>
            <li>Using the App in compliance with local laws and regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Disclaimers and Limitations</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>No Warranty:</strong> The App is provided "as is" without any warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the App will be error-free or uninterrupted.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Accuracy:</strong> While we strive to provide a reliable service, we cannot guarantee that notifications will always be delivered or that the App will function perfectly in all circumstances.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Local Authority Changes:</strong> Bin collection schedules may change due to holidays, local authority decisions, or other factors beyond our control. Users should verify collection dates with their local waste management authority.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Missed bin collections due to notification failures</li>
            <li>Fines or penalties from local authorities</li>
            <li>Data loss or corruption</li>
            <li>Device damage or malfunction</li>
            <li>Any other damages arising from use of the App</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you paid for the App (if any).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy, which explains how we handle your information when you use our App. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with our Privacy Policy.
          </p>
          <p>
            In summary: We don't collect any personal data. Everything stays on your device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Updates and Modifications</h2>
          <p>
            We may update the App from time to time to add features, fix bugs, or improve performance. Updates will be distributed through the App Store.
          </p>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. If we make material changes, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Your continued use of the App after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Termination</h2>
          <p>
            You may stop using the App at any time by deleting it from your device. We may terminate or suspend your access to the App immediately, without prior notice, if you breach these Terms.
          </p>
          <p>
            Upon termination, your right to use the App will cease immediately, and you should delete the App from your device.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>App Store Terms</h2>
          <p>
            Your use of the App is also subject to the Apple App Store Terms of Service. In case of conflict between these Terms and the App Store Terms, the App Store Terms shall prevail with respect to your use of the App Store.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            The App and its original content, features, and functionality are and will remain our exclusive property. The App is protected by copyright, trademark, and other laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction where we are located, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Severability</h2>
          <p>
            If any provision of these Terms is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions will remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@spicybackend.dev">legal@spicybackend.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2>Acknowledgment</h2>
          <p>
            By using the Bin Collection app, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and our Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 120px 0 var(--spacing-4xl);
  }

  .policy-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl);
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px var(--shadow-light);
  }

  .policy-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .policy-content section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .policy-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .policy-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .policy-content ul {
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .policy-content li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .policy-content a {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .policy-content a:hover {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .policy-content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Responsive design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-page {
      padding: 100px 0 var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .policy-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
      margin: 0 var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .policy-content h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    }

    .policy-content h2 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    }

    .policy-content ul {
      padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .policy-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .policy-content h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
